high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the microwave on the white table.
Open the microwave and take the cup out of it.
Turn around and walk towards the sink on your right.
Place the cup in the sink, wash it, and take it back out.
Take a step to the right to face the coffee maker.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed white cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the microwave on the small table across the room.
Open the microwave and take the mug out. Close the door.
Take the mug and turn around, then to the right to find the sink.
Place the mug in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the mug.
Take the mug next to you and face the coffee maker.
Put the mug under the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Get a mug for a cup of coffee.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the microwave on the table in the corner
Open the microwave and remove the mug from it
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink
Wash the mug under water in the sink then remove it
Walk a few feet to the right then turn left to face the coffee maker
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned mug in the coffee maker
